    <div id="source-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
<table><tr><td>National Clinical Guideline Centre. Lipid modification: cardiovascular risk assessment and the modification of blood lipids for the primary and secondary prevention of cardiovascular disease.  London (UK): National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE); 2014 Jul. 50 p.&nbsp;(Clinical guideline; no. 181).&nbsp;</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180713034706/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48406&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.nice.org.uk%252fguidance%252fcg181">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713034706im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
