, <a href="/web/20180713034706/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0086930&amp;fLockTerm=Risk+Assessment">Risk Assessment</a>
, <a href="/web/20180713034706/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0202236&amp;fLockTerm=Triglycerides+measurement">Triglycerides measurement</a>
, <a href="/web/20180713034706/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0920298&amp;fLockTerm=Weight+maintenance+regimen">Weight maintenance regimen</a>
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.field-content -->
                </div>
