                        <h3><a href="#">Potential Harms</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Statin therapy has been associated with the following adverse events: myalgia, myopathy, asthenia, creatine kinase elevation, elevated liver function tests, and rhabdomyolysis.</p>
<p>Refer to the "Trade off between clinical benefits and harms" sections in the full version of the original guideline document (see the "Availability of Companion Documents" field) for harms of specific interventions.</p></div></p>

