<p>National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE). Statins for the prevention of cardiovascular events. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2006 Jan. 45 p. (Technology appraisal guidance; no. 94).</p>
